Yapi Kredi to Loan $65.5 Million for Turkish Hydropower Project in Batman

-- B y   A y d a n   E k s i n
-- 
2011-02-18T10:58:10Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-18/yapi-kredi-lends-65-5-million-for-turkish-hydropower-project.html
Yapi & Kredi Bankasi AS, the Turkish
bank part-owned by  UniCredit SpA , lent $65.5 million to power
generator Fernas Enerji to finance a 49-megawatts hydropower
plant it is building in Batman in southeast Turkey.  The loan has a maturity of 10 years, Yapi Kredi said in an
e-mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Aydan Eksin at 
 aeksin@bloomberg.net  